http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Thiruvananthapuram/New-platform-inaugurated/article14000807.ece

A. Sampath, MP, inaugurated the refurbished platform of Kadakkavoor railway station at a function attended by Divisional General Manager Sunil Bajpai, and Kadakavoor panchayat president K. Vilasini. Mr. Sampath said he would take steps to provide more infrastructure facilities at the station and set up a high mast lamp. Mr. Bajpai said Railways would renovate the Sub-Registrar road leading to the station. Permission would be given to renovate the Maruthanvilakom road to the local panchayat, he said.